Package capitalism.view.tables

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommodityColumn
    A StockColumn contains the additional information needed to display a switchable graphic and to select the data item for display The data items delivered to the parent TableView for display in its cells are always strings; the type conversion is handled by the Industry class.
